---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Reserva Enviada | Lambin Suite" 
  description="Tu solicitud de reserva ha sido enviada con éxito a Lambin Suite."
>
  <Header />
  
  <main class="flex-grow flex items-center justify-center py-20 bg-navy-50/30">
    <div class="max-w-md w-full mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gold-500/15 text-gold-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto text-4xl mb-8 animate-bounce border border-gold-500/20">
        🔑
      </div>
      
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-navy-900 tracking-tight">
        ¡Reserva Recibida!
      </h1>
      
      <p class="mt-4 text-navy-700/80 leading-relaxed text-sm sm:text-base">
        Tu solicitud ha sido procesada con éxito. Nos comunicaremos contigo en los próximos minutos al celular registrado para confirmar tu llegada.
      </p>
      
      <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a 
          href="/" 
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 border border-transparent text-sm font-bold rounded-xl text-navy-950 bg-gold-500 hover:bg-gold-400 active:scale-95 transition-all duration-150 shadow-md shadow-gold-500/10"
        >
          Volver al Inicio
        </a>
        <a 
          href="https://wa.me/59170000000?text=Hola,%20acabo%20de%20enviar%20mi%20formulario%20de%20reserva%20y%20quisiera%20confirmar%20por%20aqu%C3%AD."
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 border border-navy-200/50 text-sm font-bold rounded-xl text-navy-800 bg-white hover:bg-navy-50/30 active:scale-95 transition-all duration-150"
        >
          Confirmar por WhatsApp
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>
